Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think he'll chase you forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizu-chin's words keep echoing in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disconnect from Yano's feelings now, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:54.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.79,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:06.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:12.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:20.26,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.98,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:30.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:39.78,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:44.70,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:51.84,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:58.59,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:54.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:01:00.79,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:06.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:12.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:20.26,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.98,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:30.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:39.78,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:44.70,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:51.84,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:58.59,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:13.73,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)\fscx112.5\fscy103\pos(158,384)}Episode 24 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:13.11,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, there aren't many days left in the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.24,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, if you don't hurry and make up with Yano, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you gonna get for him this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I need to start spending less and save up for a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're in the middle of a fight, Christmas is still stuck in my mind...
