Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... a notice from the hospital. Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just another one like they sent last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember how I went for another exam, and they removed all of those benign polyps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left some in because they were too small, so they're probably acting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think it'd be a good idea to get checked out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. But we're so busy with all of this moving business right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get to Tokyo, I'll take some time and go in for another examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving around Christmastime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it! It's not like I'm a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cheeky, worrying about your mother like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way... what's your pay going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much is it?
