Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it'll "do the trick"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my savings account, and I can also work part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work part-time, so don't bother with my allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to give your undivided attention to college entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come up with the money somehow if there's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I'll have a rough time straight from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take money from your bank account!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of my tuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drop out of college because of the extra work, you'll be confusing your priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... just leave my business to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already uneasy enough, leaving you here where I can't keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't say things like you'll get a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.18,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H40&\c&H000000&\fscx172.5\fscy210\b1\frz44.05\frx12\fry338\pos(344,176)}Information for Applicants
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.18,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H55&\c&H000000&\frx6\fry350\fscx92.5\fscy95\pos(341,243)\frz41.259}You'll definitely find a job perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.18,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H22&\c&H000000&\fscx76.25\fscy98.75\frz47.257\frx4\fry342\pos(482,101)}Part-Time Information Magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom was against it, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but maybe not worrying her is another way of being a good son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then going where she can keep an eye on me would be considered being a good son, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, once December comes around, there's gonna be an opening at my liquor store. We'll need some extra hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask my dad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might even increase your hourly wage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How... about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tell me you plan on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up, Moto! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually thinking of going with your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you couldn't leave Takahashi behind the other day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to keep giving you those chances right before my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much confusion right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she gets uneasy over all of those pointless things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so if she said she was leaving for Tokyo... if she said we'd have to part from one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's no way she could bear it, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With women, if you're not by their sides, you don't know where they'll go running off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lying. He's definitely lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fine? If he wants to go, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to butt in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you? That's pretty cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that when you always worked him to the bone as a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like you did with me, your actual blood-related brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pushing him around, making him your little servant, making him give you massages...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one who wanted to massage me, so I let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know. He told me you tricked him into doing it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron. I wonder what he was expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is a moron. Though I can sorta understand how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one I don't understand the most is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Moto leaves, isn't it your chance to make her yours once and for all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that he's your rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Takahashi if it's going to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want her to come to me because he's no good for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't want her to come to me because she's lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Takahashi to say that I'm the one meant for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Moto's headed to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go deciding that all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. So she is, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka, would you put on some tea for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "so she is"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy's mother always looks so flighty and up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she doesn't have her feet on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like she became an adult while still being a girl on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though in a way, I'm kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though Moto's kept a pretty firm grip on himself, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... but that's a pretty common pattern, where the child becomes much more steady if the parents are unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I hear, Moto's mom is supposedly a lot like that type of girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That type"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like his dead girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With women, if you're not by their sides, you don't know where they'll go running off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... he seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...might go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? It's cold out, so come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and make up with him! Stop him from going to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tokyo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to be anxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with saying, "if we split up, things will fall apart"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say insubstantial crap like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you if you want things to fall apart, but going about it this way is just wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry up and talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's... going to leave?
