Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice at all that Yano was going through so much right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, have you written down your choices yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see, let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why hasn't he told me a word about it?
