Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K University? What's your second choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one. I don't plan on going anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty set on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you don't get accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if that'd happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're with guys headed off to Tokyo, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to Sapporo, though it looks like about half our class wants to leave Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see what she wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I remember, she said she was going to apply to at least one Tokyo school the last time we talked about college...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become a little uneasy about all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she goes to college in Tokyo, I can say we'd only be apart for a year, and it'd be easy to persuade her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking? It should be something different right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What college do you plan on going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something more important than that right now, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... you said your parents didn't want you going to a college in Tokyo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you wanted to convince them to let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there weren't too many schools you wanted to go to here in Hokkaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since you're so good at English, you said you wanted to study English literature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, since you wanted to go to a school that stands out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might aim for one of those Christian schools where they make you dress up in those uniforms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. There's always A University, College of R, and S University. They're all in Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I have changed what school I want to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you convince your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you talk to me about that even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't tell me anything either, Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if your school won't be in Tokyo, everything's all better now that you're not with me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I express my feelings...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I love him so much, I always say the opposite...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to tell him I love him, but I'm afraid he might feel differently now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to affirm them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you love him, you become anxious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not just come right out and tell him that you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he's more important to you than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you don't want him to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hated myself the most for being so childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cause so much trouble for Yano, make him uneasy, hurt him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the more I fall in love with him, the fewer words I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to tell him what's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm the one who's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want this, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm, I'm sorry for stopping by so late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had some urgent business...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to talk about with Yano-kun right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he should be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's out...
