Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like sweet potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I came here to stop Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't really look his mom straight in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
