Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, I heard your mom's getting divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being too selfish and couldn't realize how lost and confused you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lost or confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of splitting up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... I think I was just blinded by my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My complaints and uneasiness about all the small things so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought they were all just exaggerated problems because we could be together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we were apart, they'd all go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love you, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really love you too, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I absolutely won't split up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, see? If we're honest with each other, we can hear each other perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano... if she needs your help, then go with your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, and really think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you really need to think about what's important to you and what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what choice you make, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:18:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't break away from each other so easily anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different from Nana-san. So from now, I'll wait until you come up with an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which Yano chooses, I want to believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now, let's think about what's going to happen in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the most part, I was able to convince my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was okay to apply to at most one school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you changed which school you wanted to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to go to one in Tokyo, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J University? Foreign languages?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my dream! Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were your latest T-scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese, 59...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,World History, 60...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,English, 64...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Total, {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}61{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be really tough if you don't at least get over a 70...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}10{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}% of the applicants passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...? {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}10{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}%, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fail, you'll be going to Sapporo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then are you going to change what school you want to go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you come up with another fallback school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi... if you fail, you're going to Sapporo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to Tokyo university for you, I'm going for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if my future path intersects with yours, I'll be very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely pass and go to Tokyo with you, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There's still a year, s-so it should be fine. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... others should be the ones saying that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to have aspirations to go there, and even though it seems reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one year is plenty of time for a miracle to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repeat your own words to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.21,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx181.25\fscy171.25\pos(320,2)}Sign: 1st choice J University\N2nd choice F college for W...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}1{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}st and 2nd choices are way too high for her. What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that Takahashi was a gambler like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, she told me she wasn't going to Tokyo for me, and it shocked me for a second, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:04.49,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx181.25\fscy171.25\pos(320,2)}Sign: J University
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she told me she was going for herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that she had a college she wanted to get into... she sounded hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I could believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Takahashi might be able to make such a miracle happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty big gambler too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's her influence on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi's really strong, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'm the more effeminate one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you still undecided?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also believe in whatever you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm off to Tokyo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you trying to get into the politics and economics program at W university?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the real problem here is what she's going to do if she fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she really end up at Sapporo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for me, that'd be a little troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... it's like she hasn't thought of anything but passing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she's the type who runs straight at something without looking back...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think it's bad if you don't glance back once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:22.65,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx181.25\fscy171.25\pos(320,2)}Sign: 1 K University
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like gambling... but I'm going to be a little more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret from Takahashi, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:30.87,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fscx181.25\fscy171.25\pos(320,2)}Sign: 2 College of H
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The College of H?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A college in Sapporo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put some insurance on this. This might be a first for me.
