Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to look at those.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you put down a public school and a national university?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... if a fairly good student does it, I don't see any problem with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it'd be much more advantageous if they could pick between one of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...going to do whatever I can for Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi. Want to go look for some study guides today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to raise your T-score by at least {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}1{\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}5 points, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what answer he comes up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:38.18,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite itsudemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite watashi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:49.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Koko ni ite miteite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:54.45,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mama zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:57.70,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Te no hira no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:00.62,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Afuredashisou na
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:06.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata ga kureta "hajimete"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:12.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi hitori ja kokoro ga yuretara
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:18.22,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Minna koborete shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:26.23,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata no ookina te de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:32.20,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi goto tsukamaeteite
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:37.37,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Konna ni mo konna ni mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:44.00,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tayorinai watashi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:50.55,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakedo ima wa anata no te wa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:54.59,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Sukoshi tookute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:38.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... always...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:49.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Be here... at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:54.45,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:57.70,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The "first time" you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:00.62,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,seems like it's going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.62,0:24:06.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,to overflow in the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:12.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If my heart wavered alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.13,0:24:18.22,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems like everyone would vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:26.23,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.23,0:24:32.20,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,took hold of me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:37.37,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even though, even though
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:44.00,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:50.55,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still stretched out your
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.55,0:24:54.59,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,arm and hand to me, just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.92,0:25:34.94,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HDC6CE3&\pos(437,374)\fscx108.75\fscy123.75\c&HFDE2FF&}Episode 25 Preview...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:10.07,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea what\N it meant for Yano to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.07,0:25:12.65,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I wouldn't be\N able to see him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.65,0:25:15.36,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want\N for Christmas this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:20.45,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,We can spend...\N Christmas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:24.42,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one week early, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.42,0:25:28.67,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear the\N beating of our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.67,0:25:32.13,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with\N my mom to Tokyo.
